Title: Home Sweet
Plot: When eight-year-old Jenna Wechsler dies as a result of a building explosion, Green and Cassady follow the trail of evidence to Rosalie Schaffner, the owner's ex-wife. McCoy and Rubirosa pursue Rosalie Schaffner despite a lack of concrete evidence, but the case takes a turn when Rubirosa finds a piece of evidence that points them in a new direction.
ParentalRatingReason: Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Jack Cleary, James Matthew Ryan, Ken Forman, Christopher Kromer, Curt Karibalis, Justine Caputo, Frank Biancamano, Jimmy Palumbo, Glenn Kalison, Ezra Knight, John Viener, Rob Farrior, Ron Scott, Rachel Black, Mich
